tweet: On Friday I attended the ribbon cutting of @OuterCapeHealth's new Wellfleet community health center where I was able to share the news that my amendment passed with bipartisan support. #ProtectOurCare #HealthCareWeekend

Since the start of our Congress #ForThePeople, @HouseDemocrats have been working to improve health care for all. This week I passed an amendment to provide funding for community health centers across the nation to follow the model put in place by @OuterCapeHealth. #ProtectOurCare pic.twitter.com/Bz3BEb3E2q
